  "notes": "`3klife-npc-brain` reached a real evolve blocker while validating `TASK-ATS-0007`. The ATM `registry-diff` route returned `ATM_DIFF_ATOM_NOT_FOUND` for `ATM-NPCBRAIN-0002`, even though the adopter already has governed map evidence and approved dry-run proposals. This shows that map-level evolve proof still lacks a machine-readable atom-level version lineage contract for adopter-managed atoms.",
